/ /_/ / / / /  / / / / / / /_/ /    / /_<span class="o">(</span>__  <span class="o">)</span> / / /
<span class="se">\_</span>___/_/ /_/  /_/ /_/ /_/<span class="se">\_</span>_, /    /___/____/_/ /_/  
                       /____/                       
Hooray! Oh My Zsh has been updated and/or is at the current version.
